# Third-Party Software

The SISTEMAS portable distribution bundles a number of third-party Python
packages (copied from the build environment's Python installation). Their
complete source code is available from the Python Package Index (PyPI):

    https://pypi.org/project/<package-name>/

Each package is distributed under its own license; the full license text
ships inside each package's source/wheel on PyPI.

